Akagera ni imwe muri pariki nasiyonali z'igihugu cy'u Rwanda, Iyi pariki iri ku buso bwa kilometero kare 1122<ref>https://www.rba.co.rw/post/Pariki-yIgihugu-yAkagera-iza-ku-isonga-mu-zisurwa-cyane-mu-Rwanda</ref>. Ikora ku turere twa Kayonza, [[Akarere ka Nyagatare|Nyagatare]] na [[Akarere ka Gatsibo|Gatsibo]] mu burasirazuba bw’u [[Rwanda|Rwanda.]] Ni imwe muri pariki 3 z'igihugu zisurwa cyane na ba mukerarugendo benshi, ikaba ari na yo nini.

Pariki y’Akagera igizwe n’ibiyaga 10 birimo: ikiyaga cy'[[Hema|Ihema]] cyakuye izina ku Babiligi bahashinze amahema ubwo bashakishaga isoko ya [[Nili|Nil.]] Inyamaswa ugenda uzisanga ahantu bitewe n’impamvu eshatu: aho inyamaswa ibonera [[umutekano]], aho ikura ibyo [[kurya]] n’[[ubuhehere]] buharangwa ikenera.

Abasura pariki y’Akagera bavuga ko banezezwa n'ubwoko bw'inyamaswa buyibarizwamo cyane inyamaswa eshanu (5) nini z'inkazi  arizo: [[Inkura]], [[Intare]], [[Imbogo]], [[Inzovu]] n[[Ingwe|’Ingwe]].<ref>https://www.igihe.com/ubukerarugendo/pariki-n-amashyamba/article/sura-pariki-y-akagera-umenye-ibitangaje-ku-nkura-isatura-inzovu-mutware-n</ref>

Akagera gatuwe n'amoko y'[[Inyoni zo mu Rwanda|inyoni]] agera kuri 490<ref>https://www.visitrwanda.com/destinations/akagera-national-park/</ref>
